## Auth middleware вЂ” `pkg/auth/`

Shared package cho **opaque Bearer session introspect**, tбєҐt cбєЈ backend service (trб»« auth) Д‘б»Ѓu import.

| File | MГґ tбєЈ |
|------|-------|
| `auth.go` | `InitAuth(authServiceURL)` вЂ” tбєЎo `SessionValidator` |
| `jwt.go` | `SessionValidator` вЂ” `GET /internal/session`, cache ~60s; `JWTValidator` = alias |
| `middleware.go` | Parse `Authorization: Bearer`, inject UserID (+ roles nбєїu cГі) vГ o context |
| `context.go` | `UserIDFromContext()`, `RolesFromContext()`, `HasRole()` |

Session verification flow:
```
Request в†’ Authorization: Bearer <opaque>
       в†’ SessionValidator.ParseAndValidate()
       в†’ GET {auth_service_url}/internal/session (cached ~60s)
       в†’ Extract user id в†’ inject context
```

KhГґng dГ№ng JWT/JWKS.

