## Docker build pattern

**QUAN TRб»ЊNG:** Mб»—i service import `pkg/auth/` в†’ cбє§n `replace` directive trong `go.mod`:
```
require github.com/puchidemy/puchi-backend/pkg v0.0.0
replace github.com/puchidemy/puchi-backend/pkg => ../../pkg
```

Dockerfile phбєЈi copy `pkg/` vГ o build context (build tб»« monorepo root):
```dockerfile
FROM golang:1.26 AS builder
WORKDIR /src
COPY pkg/go.mod pkg/go.sum ./pkg/
COPY app/{service}/go.mod app/{service}/go.sum ./app/{service}/
RUN cd app/{service} && go mod download
COPY pkg/ ./pkg/
COPY app/{service}/ ./app/{service}/
RUN cd app/{service} && go build -o /bin/{service} ./cmd/{service}/
```

CI matrix (`.github/workflows/backend.yml`): `context: .`, `file: app/{service}/Dockerfile`

## CI/CD

